title: Scatterlands 001 (2013) (Digital) Warren Ellis & Jason Howar
description:
CBR | English | 54 pages

Scatterlands #1
Written by Warren Ellis
Art by Jason Howard

The first section of SCATTERLANDS by Warren Ellis & Jason Howard, as serialised on warrenellis.com.  Amira is a princess of the Western Court of the Assassin King, and she's on the run, desperately searching the dead city of Bioming for a way out.  She needs to discover the reason for the world...
